get.description:
Exchanges supported
- NASDAQ
- NYSE (New York Stock Exchange)
- XETRA (German Electronic Exchange)
- ASX (Australian Stock Exchange)
- TSX (Toronto Stock Exchange)
- ENX (EuroNext)
- NSE (National Stock Exchange of India)
- LSE (London Stock Exchange)
- MOEX (Moscow Stock Exchange)
- HKEX (Hong Kong Stock Exchange)
- SIX (Swiss Stock Exchange)

Not supported.
- OSE (Oslo Stock Exchange)


`/quote/all-crypto` to get bulk crypto quotes.

If speed is key, consider using `format=csv` to return bulk quotes as CSV. CSV responses are much smaller as there is no key replication.

parameters.name: query
parameters.description: Stock/Crypto symbol or equity name to search for. I.E 'AAPL' & 'Apple' are both valid searches for 'Apple Inc.'
